OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will be cloudy but
OL,6,Fmostly dry. Turning cloudier in the
OL,7,Fafternoon and patchy rain may reach
OL,8,FOrkney for a time in the early
OL,9,Fafternoon and Shetland in the late
OL,10,Fafternoon. Fresh southeasterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will become increasingly
OL,13,Fcloudy through the evening with patchy
OL,14,Frain. Some patches of haar possible
OL,15,Fovernight with outbreaks of rain.
OL,16,FFresh southeasterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
