OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloud and rain will clear
OL,6,FOrkney early morning, Shetland in the
OL,7,Fafternoon. Dry and bright for a few
OL,8,Fhours before showery rain spreads
OL,9,Fnorth in the afternoon. Occasionally
OL,10,Ffresh winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,13,For sunny spells will follow from
OL,14,FMonday to Wednesday with showers at
OL,15,Ftimes, these occasionally heavy and
OL,16,Fthundery. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
